{
  "id": "adv_event_2211_01_03",
  "title": "勃発？\n褒め合い\nバトル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……\nそれじゃ、私はひとまずお風呂に入ってくるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…\nWell then‚ I'll go take a bath for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.0308390618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "明日のライブの準備もあるし\nいつまでも幽霊なんかで騒いではいられないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have preparations for tomorrow's live to do‚\nand we can't keep making a fuss about ghosts forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2333333333,
      "endTime": 11.6280498822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、みんなでお風呂に行こー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ let's all go to the bath together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8333333333,
      "endTime": 15.199433215400001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "は？　冗談。なんで温泉でまで\n他のやつらと顔を突き合わせなきゃなんないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Joking‚ right? Why do I have to face those other guys\neven at the hot spring?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4,
      "endTime": 21.7270519256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　でもみんな仲良くって言ってたでしょ？\n仲良くしようよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But everyone said they were getting along‚ right?\nLet's all get along!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9333333333,
      "endTime": 27.918458207500002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "げー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1333333333,
      "endTime": 29.666666666700003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "わ……分かったわ\nそういうことなら仕方ないわね、行くわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W… well‚ I get it.\nIf that's what it takes‚ then fine‚ I'll go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2333333333,
      "endTime": 38.3253970465,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
