      "text": "……私も、その『仲良く』には含まれるのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see‚ I'm included in that \"getting along‚\" huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2,
      "endTime": 49.384693861,
      "sfxList": [
        {
