    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふう、いいお湯だったわ……\n建物は古いけど、露天風呂は風情があったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ the bath was wonderful…\nThe building may be old‚\nbut the open-air bath had a certain charm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6666666667,
      "endTime": 64.5122675579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、気持ち良かった～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it felt so good~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7,
      "endTime": 68.90410423280001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "でもスリクスさん達が、お風呂に入ってる間\nずーっと黙ったままなのは、びっくりしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it was surprising that IIIX-san\nand the others remained silent while in the bath…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1,
      "endTime": 76.6936506271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、喧嘩するとまた幽霊が出るもの\n……今日だけ喧嘩しない、今日だけ文句言わない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's because if we argue‚ the ghosts will appear again.\n…Just for today‚ we won't argue‚ just for today‚\nwe won't complain…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9,
      "endTime": 84.8489114761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "……口を開けば喧嘩になるのは確定ってわけね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's a given that if we open our mouths‚\nit'll turn into an argument.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0333333333,
      "endTime": 89.2459183534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、喧嘩しないで黙ってるのと\n仲良くするのは、やっぱり違う気がするなあ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But staying silent and getting along\nsomehow feels different from each other‚ doesn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4333333333,
      "endTime": 96.85233567549999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、どうしろってのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what are we supposed to do then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666666667,
      "endTime": 99.7908390681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……そうだ！　文句ばっかり言うんじゃなくて\nお礼を言うとか、いいところを褒めてみるとか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… I've got it! Instead of just complaining‚\nwhy not say thank you or compliment something nice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100,
      "endTime": 109.2987297058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
